Base Class: Card

Properties:
    cardNumber: The unique number identifying the card.
    cardHolderName: The name of the person who owns the card.
Methods:
    makePayment(amount): Simulates making a payment of the specified amount.
    displayDetails(): Displays the card details (card number and card holder name).

Subclass: CreditCard

    Inherits all properties and methods from the Card class.
    Additional functionality specific to credit cards (amount) can be added here.

Subclass: DebitCard

    Inherits all properties and methods from the Card class.
    Additional functionality specific to debit cards (amount) can be added here.